description: Roaming the streets of Reno is Schnitzel’s Austrian Grill, the truck that’s treating Nevadans to authentic and scrumptious Austrian cuisine. Made with the highest quality and freshest ingredients, this marvelous menu offers Pork Schnitzel (tenderized pork loin that’s lightly breaded and beautifully golden), Chicken Schnitzel, and other European favorites, like Bratwurst, Hungarian Gulaschsoup, Cider-braised Sauerkraut, and more. If you’re lookin’ for deliciousness, come check out what’s cookin’ at Schnitzel’s.
name: Schnitzel's Austrian Grill
